I '''Gragn Lec''' é tl raiun di Gragn Lec tl nord dl continënt american danter [[Canada]] y [[USA]] ti raiuns dl Ontario, Québec, Minnesota, Wisconsin, Illinois, Indiana, Michigan, Ohio, Pennsylvania, New York.
[[File:Great Lakes from space.jpg|thumb|I Gragn Lec]]

Lapró aldel cinch [[Lech|lec]] danter i maius dl [[Tera|monn]]:
* Lech Superior 
* Lech Michigan
* Lech Huron
* Lech Erie 
* Lech Ontario


Le Lech Superior é le lech d’ega ducia maiú dl monn.


